# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# .gitignore — Pigeon token-economy reproducible analysis
#
# The public repository tracks only the reproducible pipeline:
#   README.md, LICENSE, CITATION.cff, analysis.qmd, PigeonEcon.Rproj, osf/README.md
# Everything below is kept locally (working archive) but excluded from Git.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# --- Published article (© publisher) ---------------------------------------
Wan et al., 2026.pdf
*.pdf

# --- Data ------------------------------------------------------------------
# Raw/original data stay local; readers obtain the dataset from OSF.
# Track only osf/README.md (the download instructions).
Data/
osf/*
!osf/README.md

# --- Private manuscripts, drafts, literature, posters ----------------------
Manuscript/
Reed Thesis/
SQAB/

# --- Original working analysis scripts (superseded by analysis.qmd) --------
R Code/

# --- Generated outputs -----------------------------------------------------
figures/
models/
*.rds
/*.html
/*_files/
analysis.html
analysis_files/
/*_cache/
.quarto/

# --- R / RStudio -----------------------------------------------------------
.Rproj.user/
.Rhistory
.RData
.Ruserdata
*.Rproj.bak

# --- OS / editor cruft -----------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
._*
Icon?
*~
.vscode/
.idea/

# --- Local tool settings ---------------------------------------------------
.claude/settings.local.json

